README

fix_oiv.py is a script which will patch an installation of the OIV app on a
Mac OS X 10.7 (Lion) system. This script should be run from the Terminal app
found in /Applications/Utilities as follows:

$ python fix_oiv.py

If you do not have direct permission to modify the OIV app but have an
administrative account on the system, then run this script using sudo as
follows:

$ sudo python fix_oiv.py




